<p>Explain the code <strong>you</strong> wrote in today's lesson. Record a short video on your phone (you can show the game running) and talk through it like you are teaching someone. Try to use these words: <strong>integrate</strong>, <strong>hit detection</strong>, <strong>bullet</strong>, <strong>score</strong>, <strong>hit effect</strong>.</p>
<blockquote>
<ol>
